# Catatan Uang - Project Overview

This is a Next.js financial tracking application with the following structure:

- `/pages`: Main page routes with corresponding API endpoints in `/pages/api`
- `/components`: Reusable UI components
- `/lib`: Utility functions, hooks, and database connection
- `/prisma`: Database schema and migrations
- `/styles`: Global CSS styles
- `/scripts`: Utility scripts for data generation and setup

The application uses:
- Next.js for frontend and API routes
- Prisma as ORM for database interactions
- NextAuth.js for authentication
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- heroicons for iconography

## Entry Points

- Main application entry: [pages/_app.js](mdc:pages/_app.js)
- Dashboard page: [pages/index.js](mdc:pages/index.js)
- Layout wrapper: [components/Layout.js](mdc:components/Layout.js)

